  <notes>
    sprk_eventlog table fields:
    - sprk_event (lookup to Event)
    - sprk_action (choice: created, completed, cancelled, deleted)
    - sprk_previousstatus (text)
    - sprk_newstatus (text)
    - sprk_timestamp (datetime)
    - sprk_user (text - user display name)

    Consider using IHttpContextAccessor to get current user info.
